## Description {#details}

Helper to keep track of a condition and if it should be treated as negated for reproducer construction.

Pred == Predicate::BAD&#95;ICMP&#95;PREDICATE indicates that this entry is a placeholder to keep the ReproducerCondStack in sync with DFSInStack.
